The two missiles hit SInnertwin and through him back. They managed to only
make him angry though, not to hurt him. He looked at Blot. "Come Blot, we
go in and rip now" he said as he transformed back into his creature mode.
He walked forward, "WE give you chance Autobot" one head said, "Now we give
you Death" yelled the other, as he began to run towards the cave.
